description:
AJCR-01 EMBROIDERED CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Chiffon Trouser: Twisted Silk Dupatta: Chiffon Color: Blue

Wrapped in the tranquility of a pre-storm sky, this ensemble shimmers like lightning about to strike. The embroidered Peshwas, a masterpiece woven from gossamer dreams, is adorned with holographic sequins, each a tiny star caught in the web of midnight blue threads. Like a queen veiled in mist, the embroidered dupatta crowns this ethereal look, making it a mesmerizing addition to your occasionwear wardrobe.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front & back bodice on chiffon
1.25 embroidered lace for bodice hem on chiffon
20 embroidered kalis for peshwas on chiffon
4.5 meter embroidered border for hemline of peshwas on chiffon
Pair of embroidered sleeves with border on chiffon
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta on chiffon with 4 side borders
1.5 meter wide width twisted silk for trouser
